metadata.name: Starving Sandwich #1
metadata.description:
Artwork #1

Starving Sandwich is a metaphore and an irony for reminding us about ourselves.

Some of us are a source of energy and a motivational force for others but we are unable to attain that to satisfy our own souls.

This image a created and designed as a reminder of that fact and is a part of a bigger collection known as Starving Souls.

Collection Desing by Hadi Pourkerman
